# 🛠️ autodep

> Automatically detect, install, and export missing Python dependencies for any project.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🔍 Scans `.py` files in your project and detects imported modules
- 📦 Installs any missing modules using `pip`
- 📄 Automatically generates or updates `requirements.txt`
- 🎨 Rich colorized CLI output using `rich`
- 🧪 Built-in test suite with `pytest`
- 🧹 Clean codebase with `flake8`, `black`, and `isort`
- 🔒 Automatically detects or sets up `.venv` environment
- 📁 CLI can run from any subdirectory of the project
- ⚙️ Makefile for fast local development & automation

---

## 📦 Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/autodep.git
cd autodep
make install
